title: Unbelievable. They’re Really Trying This (Ep 1379)
description:
In this episode, I discuss the hilariously awful attempt by the media to change their story about the Biden Crime Family. I also address the real reason the Amy Coney Barrett confirmation could change everything. 

News Picks:

“Journalists” mocked for falsely claiming the Trump healthcare plan was blank pages. 

CNN’s Chris Cuomo loses it on tv after getting busted for being a hypocrite.

The Biden campaign is desperately trying to walk back it’s threats to the oil and gas industry.


A big win for fair elections in Wisconsin. 


Rumble is growing in popularity as people grow tired of YouTube censorship.
